Welcome back to What I=E2=80=99m Hearing, a little early tonight because
I=E2=80=99m headed out of the country for the week. Box office guru Scott M=
endelson will be here on Thursday, but today I=E2=80=99m ending 2024 with m=
y annual anointment of the Hero of the Year. Drumroll please=E2=80=A6

