* The bankers who gave the production companies of LeBron James, Reese
Witherspoon, and other celebrities those inflated valuations that came cras=
hing down this year
* The word =E2=80=9Crightsizing,=E2=80=9D the lamest and most overused euph=
emism for the massive layoffs that dominated the year.

